OL,3,CSandwell Council vote Reform UK
OL,4,Cpolitician as new council leader
OL,6,FNock was selected as Reform UK's
OL,7,Fleader shortly after the local
OL,8,Felection.
OL,10,F"I want to turn the ship"
OL,12,FSpeaking after Reform's victory in
OL,13,FSandwell, Nock said "I want to turn
OL,14,Fthe ship. It's been going into a storm
OL,15,Fnow for 20, 30 years.
OL,17,F"We've got social deprivation issues
OL,18,Fthat are shocking. We've got health
OL,19,Fissues that are shocking. Education
OL,20,Fand housing issues that are shocking,
OL,21,Fand we've got to make a change."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
