OL,3,CSandwell Council vote Reform UK
OL,4,Cpolitician as new council leader
OL,6,FOutgoing Labour council leader Kerry
OL,7,FCarmichael said: "It worries me what's
OL,8,Fgoing to happen, I know the people of
OL,9,FBlackheath can be quite demanding as
OL,10,Fwell.
OL,12,F"Hopefully these guys will step up and
OL,13,Fdo the right thing for these people,
OL,14,Fincluding myself because they're my
OL,15,Fcouncillors now."
